 policy changes and the implementation of innovative solutions from nature, we can reduce major outbreaks, save some ocean ecosystems, and protect our fragile environment.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aAbalonesxDiseases. 0aCoralsxDiseases. 0aMarine ecosystem health. 0aSalmonxDiseases. 0aStarfishesxDiseases. 7aSCIENCE / Environmental Science (see also Chemistry / Environmental).2bisacsh  aanthropocene.  abiodiversity.  aclimate change.  acoral bleaching.  aglobal warming.  amarine biology.  aocean health.  aplastics.  apollution.  asea level rise.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chem., Mat.Sc, Geosc 2019 Englishz978311061064208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry,  Materials Sc, Geosc 2019z9783110606461oZDB-23-DPC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCA Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065207908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520969506zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520969506423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520969506.jpg  a978-3-11-061064-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chem., Mat.Sc, Geosc 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065207-9  UCA Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-066763-9  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DPCb2019